sequenceDiagram
    participant App as Application
    participant FR as FormatRegistry
    participant PR as ParserRegistry
    participant TP as TextParser
    participant PD as ParsedDocument

    App->>FR: detectByFilename("doc.md")
    FR-->>App: TextFormat(id="markdown")

    App->>PR: getParser(format)
    PR-->>App: MarkdownParser

    App->>TP: parse(content, options)
    TP-->>App: ParsedDocument

    Note over PD: HTML not generated yet

    App->>PD: toHtml(lightMode=true)
    PD->>PD: Generate via injected generator
    PD-->>App: "<div>...</div>"

    App->>PD: toHtml(lightMode=true)
    PD-->>App: Cached HTML (instant)
